data.description: IMAGINE waking up to this view in the morning!! Along with 1.24ac of low Maintenace land for your privacy overlooking the valley.  This amazing remodel of a 1940's bungalow home, boast a Primary Suite with walk-in closet and full bath.  Open living home with split floor plan.  2 more nice bedrooms with Bath! That includes Shower/Claw-foot Bathtub!  Nice laundry/Mud room leading to deck.  A partial unfinished walkout basement for wonderful Storage or workshop.  Fenced yard for your children and pets.      (SELLER SHARES:  We loved that we were in a smaller community with a small-town feel.  But, close to the city of Birmingham and access to bigger events, nightlife. This house is cozy, but not too small for our family. Not to cramped or limited. It works super well for our family and our neighbors are great. kids and kid friendly neighborhood and quiet when it needs to be.)
